summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning; amending Plat 306W, Page 191 of the official Land Use Map of The City of Seattle adopted by Ordinance 110570 to rezone certain property in Rainier Beach Garden Tracts from Residential, Single Family 7200 (SF 7200) to Residential, Multi-Family, Lowrise 3 (L-3) and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (Petition of B. Douglas Webb, Agent for Subdivision Management, Inc., C.F. 291038). Map Amendment No. 1.
